      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3501 - Hudhayfah ibn Mansur narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"The one who frees (a slave) is the mawla (master), and the child associates himself with whomever he wishes.\""
